doc.ContractDescription: CONTRACTOR STATEMENT OF RELEASE IN CONSIDERATION OF THE MODIFICATION(S) AGREED TO HEREIN AS COMPLETE EQUITABLE ADJUSTMENTS FOR THE CONTRACTORS INVOICE DATED JANUARY 21, 2016 FOR THE WYOMING VALLEY SANITARY UTILITY AT THE MAX ROSENN COURTHOUSE, THE CONTRACTOR HEREBY RELEASES THE GOVERNMENT FROM ANY AND ALL LIABILITY UNDER THIS CONTRACT FOR FURTHER EQUITABLE ADJUSTMENTS ATTRIBUTABLE TO SUCH FACTS OR CIRCUMSTANCES GIVING RISE TO THE PROPOSAL(S) FOR ADJUSTMENT MODIFICATION PS02. THIS MODIFICATION INCREASES THE AMOUNT BY $286.00 FROM $3,840.00 TO MAKE THE TOTAL OF THE ENTIRE CONTRACT $4,126.00. THE INCREASE IS TO COVER THE COST OF THE QUARTERLY SEWER MAINTENANCE FEES FOR THE REMAINDER OF THE CONTRACT. THE PURPOSE OF THIS MODIFICATION IS TO COVER THE SEWER MAINTENANCE FEES TO THE CURRENT WYOMING VALLEY SANITARY AUTHORITY UTILITY CONTRACT PER THE ATTACHED SCOPE OF WORK, CONTRACT GS-03P-09-QF-P-0041 AND ACCOUNT NO. 240228768-0. ALL OTHER TERMS AND CONDITIONS WILL REMAIN THE SAME AND THE PERIOD OF PERFORMANCE BEGIN DATE WILL BE 03/01/2016 AND END DATE IS 05/10/2019 REMAINS UNCHANGED. IT IS AGREED THAT THE EQUITABLE ADJUSTMENT PROVIDED FOR IN THIS MODIFICATION CONSTITUTES AN ACCORD AND SATISFACTION OF ANY AND ALL PAST, PRESENT AND FUTURE CLAIMS FOR ADDITIONAL MONETARY COMPENSATION AND TIME FOR THE ACCOMPLISHMENT OF THE WORK DESCRIBED IN THIS MODIFICATION.
